out on the BBC.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9905199633296219, \"rank\": 0.009570767901005939, \"text\": \"Maidenhead\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maidenhead_United_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9994364830329914, \"rank\": 0.0005544769391923224, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The recognition\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"chaotic but eye-catching family\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"friend celebrations\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dean seemed to take it all in his stride at a Gameswhere Covid twice nearly derailed his ambitionsof competing there,going on to win 200m freestyle goldand another in the team relay.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999431004593441, \"rank\": 5.6902596461550444e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his stride\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"a Gameswhere Covid\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"his ambitionsof\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"200m freestyle goldand\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the team relay\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember at one point my coach said that if I even make it to the start line, 'I will eat my hat',\\\" he said of a tumultuous lead-in.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"my hat\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"a tumultuous lead-in\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The build-up to Paris has not quite had the same perils, although he will not defend his individual title, having missed out to team-mates Duncan Scott and Matt Richards at the Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.588477542642471e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}, {\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"score\": 0.8167390230814645, \"rank\": 0.2243767313019458, \"text\": \"Matt Richards\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Richards_(footballer,_born_1984)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The build-up\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"the same perils\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"his individual title\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he has qualified for the 200m individual medley and will be a key facet in the relay once more.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200m individual medley\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"a key facet\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's tough when it comes down to one race and a few hundredths of a second,\\\" he said, reflecting on the British Championships.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one race\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"a few hundredths\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the British Championships\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd consistently been on the podium every year and, on the day, slightly misjudged my race tactics and will not be able to defend my Olympic title.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"my race tactics\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"my Olympic title\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's brutal and it took a bit of a reset, but I am okay now, I know what I am going after and medals remain the focus.\\\"\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"a reset\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, he pipped Scott to gold in the 200m freestyle by a whisker, and the two are expected to be closely matched in the individual medley.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999219637847956, \"rank\": 7.804198216034202e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9989983783210675, \"rank\": 0.0010025820355314698, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m freestyle\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"a whisker\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual medley\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic Games swimming schedule in full: Events, UK start times and dates Paris 2024 Olympics schedule in full: Date and time for every event Despite the rivalry, Dean, 24, said: \\\"We get on really well and message a lot.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9817966085878201, \"rank\": 0.018540898641058283, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999431004593441, \"rank\": 5.6902596461550444e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic Games swimming schedule\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"full: Events\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"Date\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"the rivalry\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We end up doing the same events at every domestic and international meet.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same events\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"every domestic and international meet\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We spend a lot of time together and often room together, so we know each other pretty well.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It takes nothing from our friendship, but he's a cut-throat athlete and will do whatever it takes to hit the wall first.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"our friendship\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"a cut-throat athlete\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2412}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amid all that, the friendship never changes, we never fall out, but the pursuit and hunger is always there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the friendship\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"the pursuit\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"hunger\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only fall-outs that might ever materialise are on the golf course, where their combined performances are infinitely less world-class.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only fall-outs\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"the golf course\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"their combined performances\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"less world-class\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember at one point my coach said that if I even make it to the start line, 'I will eat my hat' Three years his senior and with six Olympic medals to his name, Scott remains an inspiration to Dean, so too Adam Peaty, although not for the reasons you might think.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9989983783210675, \"rank\": 0.0010025820355314698, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999431004593441, \"rank\": 5.6902596461550444e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}, {\"begin\": 2906, \"end\": 2916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"Three years\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"his name\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty is bidding for a hat-trick of Olympic titles in the 100m breaststroke and, while impressed by his exploits in the water, Dean has been more blown away by his actions out of it.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.9999431004593441, \"rank\": 5.6902596461550444e-05, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"a hat-trick\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic titles\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"his exploits\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"his actions\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty has made no secret of his personal turmoil since Tokyo, the breakdown of the relationship with the mother of his son, depression and a reliance on alcohol.\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3204, \"end\": 3209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999219637847956, \"rank\": 7.804198216034202e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"no secret\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"his personal turmoil\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakdown\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"the relationship\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"the mother\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"depression\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"a reliance\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3298}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As I have got older as an athlete, I have understood more the toll that takes on you, trying for years to stay on the podium,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"the toll\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3415}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He needed to take a break, to twice miss the Worlds, but then come back as strong as I have ever seen him.\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3475}, {\"ngram\": \"the Worlds\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what inspires me more as an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain enjoyed their best ever Olympic performance in the pool in Tokyo, and Dean believes they will continue to be a force to be reckoned with alongside the more traditional powerhouses of the US and Australia.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3